STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Michael Alan FRY, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-2079 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 3, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Michael Fry appeals his judgment and sentence for possession of methamphetamine, third or subsequent offense, as a habitual felon. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
